    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It is mechanically functional but shows noticeable cosmetic wear and tear on both the exterior and interior. Some minor repairs or maintenance may be required in the near future.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained. It is mechanically sound. The interior and exterior show some minor signs of normal wear, but there is no significant damage.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find some minor stone chips on the hood and small surface scratches consistent with careful daily driving. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, showing only light wear on the driver's side bolster and steering wheel. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced regularly. It is a dependable, attractive option for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits showroom-level integrity throughout, featuring a flawless exterior profile and a cabin that remains in its original, pristine state. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and never missed a service. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. You won't find one cleaner than this! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a textbook example of Japanese over-engineering, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six engine with its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup intact. Power is managed via the robust V160 Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque distribution. The vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with a dry undercarriage, factory-spec compression across all cylinders, and a pristine cooling system with high-efficiency heat exchangers. The double-wishbone suspension geometry remains tight, providing the tactile feedback expected of a flagship grand tourer. This is a mechanically flawless, collector-grade specimen for those who demand uncompromising performance and structural rigidity.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No mechanical issues or cosmetic damage. Inspection reports available.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in a stunning Guards Red finish. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and professional-grade ceramic-coated from day one. The exterior is flawless, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or paint imperfections. Inside, the black leather interior remains in an 'as-new' state; the seat bolsters show zero wear, the buttons retain their factory tactile feel, and the cabin still carries that signature new-Porsche scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, chronologically organized service history from authorized dealerships, both original keys, and all factory manuals. There are no modifications, no track history, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that rivals its original showroom state. This specimen boasts a flawless exterior finish complemented by a meticulously preserved interior, reflecting a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. Every mechanical system has been subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure peak performance and reliability. For the discerning buyer seeking an uncompromising driving experience, this offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a vehicle of true distinction.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    }
  ],
